entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You freed Angela's husband and killed the leader of the people that kidnapped him!
entries.journal_entry_description: Kill the leader of the kidnapping cave-dwellers and end their treachery.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Although you saved the current hostages, you must make sure that this cannot happen again. To do that, eliminate their leader.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: The leader left a datapad nearby. Check it for information.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: The government of Corellia is beyond corrupt! They can exterminate families like they are vermin! I'm going to take my little family and go to live in the woods. I will have my revenge!  The world will know the name of Raynod Menar!!
entries.task02_message_box_text: The government of Corellia is beyond corrupt! They can exterminate families like they are vermin! I'm going to take my little family and go to live in the woods. I will have my revenge!  The world will know the name of Raynod Menar!!
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Commander Talte and give him the news.
